ith extra cinnamon and serve with yoghurt (optional)."}],"hintsAndTricks":["You can use your preferred brown sugar in this recipe – either regular brown sugar or a less refined option such as Rapadura sugar (Panela) or coconut sugar.","If you prefer, you can serve this pudding with custard instead of yoghurt, such as the Better-for-you custard on this recipe chip."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 20m","6 portions"]}